HEADWORD: Eugenia
<hw>Eu*ge"ni*a</hw> <pr>(⟦usl⟧*j⟦emac⟧"n⟦icr⟧*⟦adot⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. Named in honor of Prince <etsep>Eugene</etsep>
of Savoy.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of myrtaceous plants,
